<L>__{exterior milady's house day}
<A>__{armand keeps his eyes on milady's house opposite. no sign of his father. he looks about, impatient... and steps across the street to enter.}
<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior milady's house day}
<A>__{armand climbs a flight of stairs. still no sign of his father, or milady. he calls out:}
<C>__{armand}
<D>__{father?}
<A>__{worry makes him hurry. armand takes hasty steps into milady's bedroom. the first thing he sees is his own face in the mirror. the second is his father's inert body below it. armand gasps, races to his side. a thin trail of bright blood is seen briefly at the older man's ear. armand gathers his father up into his arms, and begins to weep.}
